research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_residual` produced the strongest non-gated proxy among recent architecture pivots, so the next informative move is a narrow family-specific stabilization pass rather than abandoning it after one prototype result. The current trunk rank formula likely underpowers the dense trunk under the strong EF=16 recipe by collapsing to a near-minimal rank, so increasing the default trunk capacity should remove more shared dense structure before sparse residual coding and improve FVU at fixed K=128.","summary":"Strengthen the internal low-rank trunk in `lowrank_residual` and rerun the same K=128 proxy comparison under the shared best signum recipe. This keeps the round focused on one architecture-family code change with no launcher or metric changes.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"I kept the round to one primary change inside the incubating `lowrank_residual` family, avoided another minor gated tweak, and verified the edited model still passes a local forward/backward smoke test.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"HOOKPOINTS","value":"layers.[3].self_attn.o_proj"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Adjusted `lowrank_residual` trunk sizing to `min(d_in, max(2*k, d_in//4))` so the dense trunk is not implicitly weakened by the shared EF=16 recipe.","Local smoke test after the edit succeeded for `lowrank_residual` forward/backward, with trunk rank 256 at `d_in=1024, k=128`.","This round isolates a family-specific stabilization hypothesis for `lowrank_residual` after its initial proxy beat `jumprelu` but remained well behind gated."],"next_hypotheses":["If the stronger-trunk `lowrank_residual` materially improves proxy FVU, keep incubating the family and then explore lower K within this family or promote to full if the gain is large enough.","If quality stays similar but throughput regresses, follow with a targeted `edit_perf_code` round rather than treating the family as architecturally weak.","If the stronger trunk still leaves `lowrank_residual` clearly uncompetitive, pivot to a different fundamentally new architecture family instead of returning to gated-local tuning."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
