research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0093_repair_1.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The round 93 crash was a pure implementation gap: `two_code_residual_vq` was missing from architecture validation and SAE factory dispatch. Registering the architecture and adding a minimal runnable two-code residual-VQ sparse coder under `sparsify/` should unblock the original `K=40, EF=12` proxy experiment without changing its intended design.","summary":"Patched the existing experiment target so `two_code_residual_vq` can instantiate and train: added the architecture to config validation, wired factory dispatch, and implemented a minimal `TwoCodeResidualVQSparseCoder` that composes two hard codebook selections before sparse residual correction. Local smoke test passed for config validation, factory lookup, forward, and backward.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"unblock_run","family_name":"two_code_residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"Kept the repair scoped to `sparsify/` and preserved the original experiment target and env overrides. Verified the new class on a local instantiate/forward/backward smoke test; the next likely blocker, if any, would be a deeper training-time issue rather than the previous unknown-architecture crash.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_code_residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"40"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 93 repair attempt 1 fixed a concrete registration blocker for `two_code_residual_vq` under `sparsify/` only.","Added `two_code_residual_vq` to `TrainConfig` architecture validation and `_get_sae_class` dispatch.","Implemented a minimal runnable `TwoCodeResidualVQSparseCoder` by extending the existing residual-VQ pattern with a second hard codebook/router stage before sparse residual coding.","Local smoke test passed: config validation, factory dispatch, forward, and backward all succeeded for `architecture=two_code_residual_vq`, `k=40`, `expansion_factor=12`."],"next_hypotheses":["Re-run the original round 93 proxy target unchanged now that the unknown-architecture crash is repaired.","If the next run crashes again, keep the experiment fixed and patch only the concrete new traceback in `sparsify/` as repair attempt 2.","If the run completes, judge `two_code_residual_vq` on low-K quality at the exact `(K=40, EF=12)` comparison point before any further architecture work."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
