research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0093.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Single-code `residual_vq` was clearly too coarse at low K, and both routed and residual-magnitude alternatives have now failed to improve the `K=40, EF=12` local frontier. A real `two_code_residual_vq` prototype that composes two hard codebook selections before the sparse residual stage is the next informative architecture move because it strengthens the discrete trunk without raising K or EF.","summary":"Implement `two_code_residual_vq` under `sparsify/` and run its first proxy comparison at `K=40, EF=12` with the unchanged `signum`/`lr=1.6e-3`/`auxk_alpha=0` recipe. This uses a fundamentally different architecture at the exact active comparison point and avoids more same-family local tuning after extended stagnation.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"two_code_residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is a genuine architecture change at the same `(K, EF)` target and directly addresses the current failure mode of weak low-K discrete capacity. The main risk is another weak first prototype, but it is more informative than further K mapping on families that have already stalled.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_code_residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"40"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 93 revisits the blocked `two_code_residual_vq` direction as the next fundamentally different low-K architecture move after routed and lowrank_residual both failed to beat the `K=40, EF=12` local baseline.","The target stays fixed at `K=40, EF=12` so the signal is directly comparable within the active low-K lane."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_code_residual_vq` at `K=40, EF=12` is competitive, keep the family fixed and test `K=32, EF=12` to see whether the stronger discrete trunk improves the lower-K Pareto tradeoff.","If it runs cleanly but is weak, archive the discrete residual-VQ branch and free incubation capacity for a different low-K family rather than continuing more residual-VQ variants."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
