research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0029.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 28 showed that `whitened_topk` is not worth continuing: under a matched probe it failed catastrophically, so the next and only remaining useful question in this probe slot is whether a different directly compatible support-selection variant has any architectural merit at all. `gated` preserves the same static-dictionary weighted-sum reconstruction form as `topk` while changing only how support is selected and scaled, so this round asks a single yes/no question: is `gated` competitive enough under a matched K128/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF12 probe to justify any future follow-up.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe on `gated`. Keep `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and the current stabilized runtime/aux recipe fixed, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `topk` to `gated` to test whether this directly export-compatible family is worth continuing.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the matched-probe rule by changing only the architecture axis, keeps the core mainline recipe fixed, and selects a family that remains compatible with LUTurbo's static-vector weighted-sum deployment contract. The main risk is that the extra gating branch may add training complexity without improving quality or runtime-aligned sparsity behavior, but that is exactly the family-worthiness question this probe is intended to answer before returning to the topk mainline.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 28 ruled out `whitened_topk` as a promising matched probe candidate because it was massively worse than the topk control.","`gated` remains directly compatible with LUTurbo deployment because the final reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over a static decoder library with fixed `K`; the change is confined to encoder-side gating and support scoring.","Judge this round as a pure family-worthiness probe against the stabilized K128 topk control: if it is clearly worse or unstable, archive it and return to topk next round; if it is competitive, record that but still return to the mainline per policy."],"next_hypotheses":["If `gated` is clearly worse than matched `topk`, archive it immediately and return to the topk mainline next round.","If `gated` is competitive but not clearly better, record it as a plausible alternative family and still return to the topk mainline next round.","If `gated` beats the matched `topk` control, schedule at most one later follow-up after the mandated return to the mainline."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/round_summaries/round_0116.json:37:        "key": "ARCHITECTURE",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0172.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `{c_m}` is a static soft-codebook library, and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; the gate only changes single-sample support weighting before top-k, not the exported decoder basis. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one static trunk lookup plus one static codebook lookup plus one sparse weighted sum over a static residual library, so inference still reduces to finite weighted sums over fixed vector banks. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost is expected to remain within the `≤ 1.5×h×n` hard budget because it adds one gate scorer on top of the already-feasible `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` path while staying below the current two-stage mainline’s selector complexity. The single question is whether the soft-codebook coarse branch remains worthwhile with a cheaper gated single-stage selector, or whether the current two-stage refinement is still clearly necessary.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` is clearly worse than the two-stage mainline in both FVU and runtime metrics, discard this family and return to `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round.","If it is modestly worse in FVU but materially better in throughput or total runtime, keep it as a lower-complexity compatible reserve branch, but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy.","If it is unexpectedly close to the mainline at lower selector complexity, allow at most one later family-specific follow-up after the required return to the mainline."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility: `扩展兼容`. Export path is static trunk library + static soft-codebook library + static residual dictionary; gating affects only online selection, not decoder exportability.","This round is a strict matched architecture probe: keep `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` explicitly pinned, and change only `ARCHITECTURE`.","Evaluate with `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total runtime cost rather than FVU alone; small quality changes with noticeably worse runtime are negative."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe. Repeating `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` has already failed twice on policy-detection rather than science, so the highest-value remaining matched probe is a nearby soft-codebook selector variant that should still be budget-feasible and avoids the same controller edge case. `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` directly tests whether the coarse codebook branch is the real source of value while simplifying the residual selector relative to the current mainline.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe on `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` with the `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, `LR=3.0e-3` mainline recipe fixed. This cleanly tests whether a softer codebook-plus-gated single-stage architecture is worth any continued attention under LUTurbo-compatible low-EF constraints.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0195.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库中的固定向量，alpha_i 是每个样本在线选择得到的稀疏系数，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为直接兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，最朴素的 topk 单库架构是否仍值得作为极低部署成本、低选择成本的 LUTurbo 备选；若其 FVU 相比 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显恶化，则说明 low-rank trunk 与 coarse branch 不是锦上添花，而是当前可用性的必要结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 topk 明显劣于 lowrank_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 topk 以更低部署成本和更快训练吞吐表现出可接受 FVU，可将其保留为最简直接兼容基线支线。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","topk 的导出路径是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容。","r192-r194 已逐步验证去掉 stage2、去掉 soft codebook、再改成 factorized scorer 都会带来明显 FVU 损失；本轮进一步测试去掉 low-rank trunk 后，最简单单库家族是否还有保留价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，问题单一明确：最简直接兼容单库架构在当前低 EF regime 下是否还有 LUTurbo 价值。它不追求取代主线，而是为‘低成本极简基线是否应继续占据搜索注意力’给出清晰结论。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 topk，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即最简单的 LUTurbo 直接兼容单库方案是否仍值得继续保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0084.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` has now produced a smooth non-dominated low-K curve through `K=7,6,5` under a fixed recipe, so the next single-variable probe should reduce only `K` to `4` and test whether this family can directly replace the current `K=4` anchor rather than only interpolating above it.","summary":"Run one parameter-only experiment at `K=4` with `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed. Success criterion: beat the current `K=4` frontier anchor FVU (`0.14181029796600342`) and promote this family from a lower-K interpolator to the direct `K=4` owner if it lands below that mark.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"frontier_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This remains the cleanest continuation of the current signal: one family, one recipe, one variable. `K=5` was clearly below the `K=4` anchor, so a same-K test at `K=4` is now the highest-value question before pushing to more speculative family changes.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"4"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 84 should be a controlled parameter-only probe at `K=4` for `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` after confirmed non-dominated points at `K=5` and above under the fixed `EF=12` / `signum` / `LR=3.2e-3` / `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` recipe.","The success criterion shifts from interpolation to direct replacement: if `K=4` beats the current `K=4` anchor FVU (`0.14181029796600342`), this family should take over the `K=4` frontier slot rather than merely extending the curve above it."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=4` wins, test `K=3` under the same fixed recipe to see whether the family can extend below the current ultra-low-K lane.","If `K=4` is very close but slightly behind the incumbent anchor, do one confirmatory rerun at `K=4` before concluding the family tops out at `K=5`.","If `K=4` clearly loses, conclude this family's useful low-K frontier ends at `K=5` and shift exploration to a new family or mechanism."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/round_summaries/round_0062.json:29:        "key": "ARCHITECTURE",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0123.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 下该 family 的 selection_cost 约 1.25x，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束；而 signum 的 LR 细扫结果显示 3.0e-3 仍优于 2.7e-3 和 2.4e-3，说明 signum 轴基本洗净。本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family/K/EF 不变的前提下，切换到 adam 并联动使用更保守的 1.0e-3 学习率，测试是否能改善收敛质量，而不是继续在 signum 上做低收益细扫。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam@1.0e-3 明显落后且曲线无额外改善趋势，则恢复 signum 为主线并停止继续扫 optimizer。","若 adam@1.0e-3 曲线更平滑但收敛偏慢，可在同一 optimizer 下补一个更高 LR 点如 1.5e-3。","若 adam 与 signum 的最终 FVU 接近但训练时间更长，则把 adam 视为负面信号并回到 K 轴比较 96 vs 128 的系统性价比。"],"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，兼容性仍为扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + residual 字典库。","signum 在 K=128、EF=2 下的 LR 细扫已给出负面信号：2.4e-3 和 2.7e-3 都未超过 3.0e-3，因此本轮转入 optimizer 轴。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，判断收益是否来自更优优化而非更长训练。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"遵守了主线推进与兼容性约束，family/K/EF 均保持不变。此轮把 optimizer 作为主变量，并按运行时允许的例外联动 LR 以避免对 adam 使用明显失配的 signum 学习率；风险是 adam 可能在该 regime 下更慢，但这是当前比继续细扫 signum 更有信息量的一步。","summary":"停止继续细扫 signum 学习率，转而在同一可行主线 family 上测试 optimizer 轴：固定 K=128、EF=2，仅切到 adam 并配 1.0e-3 学习率，验证是否存在更好的收敛质量/成本权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0197.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库中的固定向量，alpha_i 是经 gate 调制后的在线稀疏系数。gate 只改变选择与系数计算路径，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性为直接兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，gated 是否能在仍满足选择成本预算（EF=2 下约 1.0x h×n）的情况下，相比 topk 提供更好的 FVU；若它仍明显落后于 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则说明纯单库 gated 路线在当前低 EF regime 下也不值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 gated 仍明显劣于 lowrank_residual / lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 gated 相比 topk 有稳定收益但仍远逊于 low-rank family，可将 gate 只视为 selector-side 局部技巧，而非主线候选。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为它们在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 超过 1.5×h×n 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","gated 的导出路径是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容。","r195 topk 已在当前 regime 下被 discard，r196 factorized_topk 更弱；本轮补完直接兼容单库路线中 gate 调制是否值得保留。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是一个严格单变量的 matched probe，问题明确：单库 gated 是否比 plain/factorized topk 更有保留价值。它不改变部署形式，只检查 gating 这一 selector 机制本身；在当前已经基本排空更便宜单库路线后，这个 probe 能给直接兼容路线更完整的结论。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：将主线切到 gated，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构是单一静态字典库上的有限稀疏加权和，属直接兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即单库 gated selector 是否足以让该 family 继续作为 LUTurbo 低成本候选。","touched_files":[]}
